    <div class="content">
      <div class="hero-section">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          Built by Experts, <br />Powered by <span class="gradient-text">AI</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          We're a team of sustainability experts, AI researchers, and engineers on a mission to
