      <div class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our <span class="gradient-text">Story</span></h2>
        <div class="section-content">
          <p>
            blipee was born from a simple observation: while companies wanted to be more
            sustainable, they struggled with the complexity, cost, and overhead of traditional
            sustainability operations. Teams spent countless hours on manual tracking, compliance
            monitoring, and data analysis—time that could be better spent on strategic initiatives.
          </p>
          <p>
            We asked ourselves: what if AI could handle all of that? What if sustainability
            operations could be automated, optimized, and running 24/7 without human intervention?
            That's when we created blipee—an autonomous AI workforce specifically designed for
            sustainability.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, our 8 specialized AI agents work around the clock for organizations worldwide,
            delivering an average of 18% cost savings, 98.5% forecast accuracy, and 85% time
            reduction in sustainability operations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
