      <div class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our <span class="gradient-text">Journey</span></h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Foundation</div>
              <div class="timeline-description">
                blipee founded with a vision to automate sustainability operations through AI. First
                three agents developed: ESG Chief of Staff, Carbon Hunter, and Compliance Guardian.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Platform Launch</div>
              <div class="timeline-description">
                Full platform launched with 8 autonomous AI agents. Introduced Prophet-style
                forecasting models with 98.5% accuracy and cross-org benchmarking capabilities.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-title">Scale & Innovation</div>
              <div class="timeline-description">
                Expanded globally, serving organizations across multiple industries. Introduced
                blipee Assistant for natural language querying and enhanced predictive capabilities.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Join Our <span class="gradient-text">Mission</span></h2>
        <div class="section-content" style="text-align: center;">
          <p>
            We're always looking for talented individuals who are passionate about sustainability
            and AI. If you want to be part of the team building the future of sustainable
